project.name: WildFly
project.description: The WildFly project produces powerful, modular and lightweight application server that helps you build amazing applications. The project has an over twenty year history since its founding as the JBoss Application Server project. It is one of the open source projects sponsored by the Commonhaus Foundation.
project.license_type: Primarily ASL 2.0, some MIT. No non-permissive licensing.
